# AI Legal Assistant (Graduation Project)

Mobile-first legal consultation app featuring AI chat, lawyer discovery, and booking flows.

## Projects
- **Flutter app:** `FlutterFrontEnd/virtual_lawyer`
- **Web prototype:** `front-end/Graduation-Project-main`

## Tech Stack
- Flutter (Dart)
- React + Vite + Tailwind CSS

## Getting Started

### Flutter
```bash
cd FlutterFrontEnd/virtual_lawyer
flutter pub get
flutter run
```

Web Frontend
```bash
cd front-end/Graduation-Project-main
npm install
npm run dev
```

Configuration
```bash
Create a .env file if you have any API keys or configuration.
```
